document.full_text: francesca schiavone's 6-3, 2-6, 6-4 victory over jelena jankovic put her into a quarterfinal match with no. 14 anastasia pavlyuchenkova, who overwhelmed no. 3 vera zvonareva, 7-6 (4), 2-6, 6-2,  earlier in the day.
document.title: after zvonareva's loss, schiavone moves into role of favorite
